answers.answer: Hello,You should be worried now.  560 is dangerously high.  Actually anything above 300 is dangerously high.Please go to the emergency room.You need insulin urgently.  You are risking diabetic ketoacidosis, which can be fatal.Do not eat any carbs or drink anything sweet.  Just drink water.  Please go to the emergency room NOW.Let us know how you go and that you are ok.
You need to worry when your BG is over 140... you need to take action when its 200.... when its 300 time to think about the ER unless you are on the way down... at 500 you need to be in the ER.
your body converts ALL carbohydrates to blood sugarALL CARBOHYDRATES raise BG  whole wheat raises BG, fruit raises BG, rice raises BG, rice even brown rice raises BG. fruit juice raises BG.
